1
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,100
Your Highness.

2
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,700
Paying my respects to Consort Yu.

3
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:21,160
I haven't seen you for a few days.

4
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,770
You've become quite plump.

5
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:26,280
It seems the First Prince treats you well.

6
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,880
His Highness only considers that

7
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:31,400
I am his only personal maid.

8
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,960
He is indeed lenient with me.

9
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,100
I am favored by Your Highness,

10
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,620
and dare not slack off.

11
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,160
What?

12
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,920
Are you feeling unwell?

13
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,079
Thank you for your concern, Your Highness.

14
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,960
I have no other symptoms.

15
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,680
This pill

16
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,360
can temporarily relieve your itching.

17
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,000
Didn't Your Highness say

18
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:15,250
the time limit is one month?

19
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,760
I said

20
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:20,079
you will die in a month.

21
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:23,730
But I never said the poison wouldn't flare up.

22
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,760
Consort Yu is so thorough.

23
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,800
What is she plotting?

24
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,370
If she doesn't trust me,

25
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,760
it will be inconvenient for me to move around the palace.

26
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,220
Thank you, Your Highness.

27
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:40,400
This antidote is very complicated to make.

28
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,240
Don't waste my efforts.

29
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:48,650
I will follow your teachings, Your Highness.

30
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:52,960
Right.

31
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:56,720
I heard Yunchuan is studying music recently.

32
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:01,040
His Highness got a new guqin,

33
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,240
composed a new piece,

34
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,520
and plays it when he has time.

35
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,100
There is nothing unusual.

36
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,160
Yes.

37
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:11,440
Yunchuan is very fond of music.

38
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,600
Although His Majesty dislikes singing and dancing,

39
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,120
I like it.

40
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:21,000
I hope Yuze Palace will have

41
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:23,610
music and singing every night from now on.

42
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,880
Who else wants one?

43
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,880
I do! I do!

44
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,640
Take it easy.

45
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,300
Give me one.

46
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,290
Who else?

47
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:07,940
Ling Xuele.

48
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:09,920
What is it?

49
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,680
What are those people doing?

50
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,330
They came to me for clothes.

51
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,320
My brother has a clothing shop

52
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,440
in the city.

53
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,600
So you've been running out these days

54
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,530
because of this.

55
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,460
Although I work in the palace,

56
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,360
I'm just a lowly maid.

57
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,160
I can't expect to cling to any powerful people.

58
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,920
So I want to earn some money

59
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:35,400
to make plans for the future.

60
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,760
But you know,

61
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:41,640
His Highness has always liked peace and quiet.

62
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,720
If you need money,

63
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,120
I can just give you

64
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,880
some extra allowance every day.

65
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:46,740
Your Highness.

66
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,480
I acted improperly.

67
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,280
Please forgive me.

68
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,000
But,

69
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,240
rewards from others

70
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,800
are never as satisfying as money earned by oneself.

71
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,330
Besides,

72
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,170
the fabric of my clothes is unique.

73
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,260
Alright, alright.

74
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,340
No need to explain.

75
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,600
Just keep a low profile from now on.

76
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,240
This is the royal palace, after all.

77
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:11,170
It's not a place for your business.

78
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,320
Thank you, Your Highness.

79
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,320
I will be careful.

80
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:14,930
Let's go.

81
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,640
By the way,

82
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:18,490
remember

83
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:21,360
to send them all away before His Highness returns.

84
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,090
You may rise.

85
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,300
Take care, Your Highness.

86
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,860
Take care, Your Highness.

87
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,220
Ladies.

88
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:38,600
You have worked in the palace for a long time,

89
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:41,059
so you must be very familiar with its layout.

90
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:44,200
Besides the four main gates,

91
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,090
are there any other entrances?

92
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:49,120
It's indeed hard to bring outside clothes into the palace now.

93
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,080
There is a side door on the north side of the estate.

94
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,640
Few people go there.

95
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,600
Only maids and eunuchs use it.

96
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,920
And we know the guard there very well.

97
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,650
You can go in and out from there.

98
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,450
Thank you, sisters.

99
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,080
Does anyone else want clothes?

100
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,600
Give me two pieces.

101
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,560
Me too.

102
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,000
Okay.

103
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,760
I only heard that my brother

104
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,520
was sent out of the palace right after birth.

105
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,280
Since no one mentioned him later,

106
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,540
I was a little curious.

107
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,450
Are you out of your mind?

108
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,400
He's back.

109
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,330
What will you do?

110
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,680
With him back,

111
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,000
Father won't stare at my studies all day.

112
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,060
Isn't that better?

113
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,600
You!

114
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,640
He is the legitimate son.

115
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,920
The late queen was

116
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,650
your father's favorite woman.

117
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,840
If it wasn't for the difficult labor,

118
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,520
which got him labeled as a jinx,

119
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:40,250
he wouldn't have been sent away for so many years.

120
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,680
Life and death are fated.

121
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,880
Those sorcerers just like to stir up trouble.

122
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,600
They made up this jinx excuse.

123
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,400
And Father actually believed it.

124
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,130
Do you know what you are saying?

125
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,120
If anyone else hears this,

126
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,380
you'll lose your head!

127
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,900
Calm down, Mother.

128
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,480
I'm only saying this in front of you.

129
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,480
My sister has been dead for years.

130
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,360
I've served His Majesty for a long time,

131
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,960
but I'm still just a consort.

132
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,920
If you don't work harder,

133
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,560
how can I help you fight for

134
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:15,240
the position of Crown Prince in the future?

135
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:17,040
The maids and eunuchs

136
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:20,040
are secretly discussing Yunchuan's background.

137
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,930
They say he's a jinx who caused Queen Yun's death.

138
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,440
He was sent out of the palace

139
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,200
when he was just a baby.

140
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:30,280
Good thing Yunchuan grew up outside the palace.

141
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:34,080
That's why he has a gentle temper and is skilled in both pen and sword.

142
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,780
If he grew up in the palace,

143
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,880
wouldn't he be like King Yunqiu?

144
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:40,140
The people of the world

145
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:42,860
would suffer countless generations of war.

146
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:56,960
Your Highness,

147
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,620
be careful!

148
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,040
Where are we?

149
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,340
Your Highness!

150
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,620
Your Highness!

151
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,730
Be careful, Your Highness!

152
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:07,840
Slow down!

153
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,600
Mother!

154
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,640
Mother!

155
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,160
Mother!

156
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,240
Mother!

157
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:29,720
Mother!

158
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,320
Mother!

159
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:35,740
Your Highness!

160
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:36,920
Mother.

161
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:40,760
Your Highness.

162
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:41,320
Mother.

163
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:45,200
Mother.

164
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,290
Mother, please don't leave me.

165
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:50,480
Mother.

166
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:55,380
Your Highness.

167
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,340
Your Highness.

168
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,640
I made you some hangover soup.

169
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:23,120
Drink some to sober up.

170
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,260
Your Highness.

171
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:34,880
Were you thinking of the late Queen Yun?

172
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:41,220
I've never seen my own mother.

173
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,620
I don't know her voice,

174
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,400
nor her face.

175
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,320
Miss her?

176
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,210
How could I miss her?

177
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,180
I heard the servants in the palace say

178
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,840
that right after you were born,

179
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,570
you were sent to Wuya Mountain.

180
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,240
Someone who,

181
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:04,770
caused his mother's death right after birth,

182
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,620
deserves to be abandoned.

183
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:11,220
Do you also believe in such superstitions, Your Highness?

184
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:13,900
What does it matter if I believe it or not?

185
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,680
Then, Your Highness,

186
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,890
have the people close to you

187
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:22,000
suffered disasters because of you?

188
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,600
Has Wuya Mountain

189
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:28,060
ever faced disasters because of you?

190
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:34,050
Since they haven't,

191
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:36,720
then this title of jinx is pure nonsense.

192
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,260
How could you understand?

193
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:43,080
A lonely person

194
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:45,320
with nowhere to come from

195
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,680
and nowhere to go.

196
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,840
Even if I dream of my mother,

197
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:52,440
I still can't touch her hand

198
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,570
or see her face clearly.

199
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,120
Your Majesty.

200
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,800
I wonder where that child ran off to again.

201
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:09,000
I'll go look somewhere else.

202
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,440
Pingle.

203
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,440
Mother.

204
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:22,600
I know I was wrong.

205
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,520
Have you finished your homework

206
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,960
before coming out to play?

207
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,800
I wasn't just playing.

208
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:32,160
I want to be like Father,

209
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:35,080
marching with the army to fight enemies

210
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,760
and protect Xuecang.

211
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,120
Pingle.

212
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,920
Do you know that a nation's strength

213
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:50,010
is not just about winning battles?

214
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,140
More importantly,

215
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:53,120
it's about winning the hearts of the people.

216
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:55,280
The people are the foundation of the state.

217
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:56,880
When the foundation is solid, the state is peaceful.

218
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:59,200
Xuecang has countless brave soldiers.

219
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:02,480
They will take on the responsibility of defending our country.

220
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,160
As for you,

221
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:05,540
what you must do

222
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:08,320
is learn how to safeguard this homeland

223
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,570
and keep it safe for a long time.

224
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:12,480
So our people in Xuecang

225
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,360
can live in peace and prosperity,

226
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:16,440
free from the burdens of war.

227
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,380
Do you understand?

228
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:19,680
Mother,

229
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,720
I think I understand.

230
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:39,840
I understand.

231
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:43,010
Of course I understand.

232
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:46,540
I understand better than Your Highness.

233
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:51,200
Watching your own parents

234
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:53,960
get murdered right before your eyes.

235
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:54,600
Kill!

236
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,000
I will fight to the death!

237
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,680
I will never be a prisoner of Yunqiu.

238
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:00,320
Kill!

239
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:01,080
Father!

240
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,600
Mother!

241
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:05,360
That fear.

242
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:11,660
Your Highness,

243
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:13,300
do you know?

244
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,640
Not back yet.

245
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,160
Not back yet.

246
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:40,000
Your Highness,

247
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,200
you are finally back.
